sellerCard.oneLiner: Architect, dotnet, CSharp, Angular, Azure, DevOps, React, Flutter
sellerCard.description: Highly motivated Software Architect with over 15 years of experience in designing and developing scalable software systems. Skilled in using agile methodologies, C#, Asp dot net, .Net core, Angular, React, React Native, Flutter, SQL, JavaScript, jQuery, Microservices, Azure DevOps, CMS, and Azure Cloud Platforms. Passionate about learning new technologies and upskilling teams for successful project execution.

description.content:
Are you looking for a professional React JS developer who can help you build a top-quality website or application? Look no further! With over 13 years of experience in the industry, I am a highly skilled software architect who can provide you with the expertise you need to take your project to the next level.


What you'll get with my service:

  • A mobile-friendly and responsive website that looks great on all devices.
  • Cross-browser support to ensure your website is accessible to everyone.
  • Professional quality output that meets the highest industry standards.
  • High-performance output for a seamless user experience.
  • Pixel-perfect design that accurately represents your brand.


Why choose me:

  • Your project will be handled by a well-experienced professional software architect.
  • I follow industrial best practices and standards.
  • I provide regular updates and communication throughout the project to ensure your satisfaction.


What I need from you:

  • Your project idea or design requirements.
  • Logos and images.
  • Text content for pages.
  • Reference sites if there are any.


Contact me today to discuss your project and take the first step towards success with React JS.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is the react version
questionsAndAnswers.answer: It will be latest version by the time of the order

packageList.title: Starter application
packageList.description: All you need to launch your company website with up to 5 static pages using your preferred design

packageList.title: Moderate application
packageList.description: Dynamic web application with API integration using your preferred design up to 7 pages

packageList.title: Complete static application
packageList.description: Full functioning website with custom API implementation up to 10 pages
